biotools.summary: CytoBrowser is a browser-based collaborative annotation platform for whole slide images. It can be used for fast and accessible collaborative online visualization, assessment, and annotation of very large microscopy images, including, but not limited to, z-stacks (focus stacks) of cytology or histology whole slide images.
